<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.2">
<l>pūṅkuruntocit tāṉaikāyntari māccekut</l>
<l>tāṅkuvēḻat tiṉkompukoṇṭu vaṉpēymulai</l>
<l>vāṅkiyuṇṭavav vāyaṉiṟkaviv vāyaṉvāy</l>
<l>ēṅkuvēyṅkuḻa leṉṉōṭā ṭumiḷamaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having broken the budding kuruntu, killed an elephant,</l>
<l>Conquered a hostile horse, then plucked the tusk from the elephant,</l>
<l>When he, whose lovely lips latched and sucked the powerful demon’s breast,</l>
<l>Stays [near], the bamboo flute that sounds at this herder’s lips</l>
<l rend="indent">moves in madness with me.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
